{
  "stem": "18770.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There isn't that cohesion anymore and that particular vibrancy of that feeling that there is a period where maybe the quality of this world is going to change.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I do realize in retrospect that's a very narrow Western world.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Nobody's concerned about what happens to the Arabs in Algeria or the blacks in Africa.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But nevertheless, for a child, for an idealistic child, there is that feeling that a better world is coming.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's not the way history particularly seems to unfold.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it's almost like-- I mean, I remember, for instance, near the end of the war going to the movies with my father.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to have these theaters that showed newsreels only before the days of television-- only newsreels.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a theater called the Newsreel Theatre.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they were showing this little film about how the United Nations was going to work.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'll never forget it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It probably exists in some archive somewhere.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Two guys on the subway, and one is completely cynical and saying, oh yeah, it's going to-- I says, yes, because if there are bad nations, the good nations will come together.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they will see that bad nations never do anything again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's that kind of energy, you know?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That kind of feeling about a new world, which if you lived through that time and then see the world that follows, while some good things happen, obviously, that dream is not fulfilled.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And to this day, I have missed that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I don't miss the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I miss the fact that-- that sense of community, that sense of purpose, that sense of a defining good has eked out of our lives more and more.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Good questions.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
